      },
      "execution_count": 4,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "5.2 Typographical Sanitization and Numeric Conversion"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "kNdeIYlQG80E"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "* Removing commas (BR standard) and inserting periods (US/Python standard);\n",
        "* Transforming the string into an auditable mathematical float."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "_QtLDqvTHEmx"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df['Net_Revenue'] = df['Net_Revenue'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '.').astype(float)\n",
        "df['EBIT'] = df['EBIT'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '.').astype(float)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Uiq2gxE4FVbb"
      },
      "execution_count": 5,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 6. Main Feature Engineering"
