        "## 10. Storytelling (Conclusion)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dA5xWWmRSUyF"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "* Despite the profitability explosion in 2022 (peaking at nearly 49%), **the Coefficient of Variation exceeding 0.30x (30%)** classifies the company's operation as highly cyclical and volatile.\n",
        "\n",
        "* Projecting the company's future *valuation* anchored in the 2022 historical ceiling would be a fatal modeling error.\n",
        "\n",
        "* The responsible analyst must converge future cash flow ($FCFF$) assumptions to the historical average (36.52%), keeping the 20.96% floor as a mandatory stress test for the approval of any investment thesis, ensuring protection against tail risk."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "uclKtAAbSfAy"
      }
